@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kqmfec(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(tmp)
    v0 = 0.99
    v2 = ((v0 + wp.sin(tmp + 0.36)) - wp.abs(v1))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp((v2 + 0.12 + v1 + 0.79)))
    v0 = (v0 + wp.cos(wp.sin(v0 + 0.35)))
    tmp = 0.84
    v2 = (v0 + (wp.sin(v1 + 0.14) / 0.76))
    data[tid] = v0
